{"tid":730630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"源頭大陸污染不減 兩電加價難改善空氣","createTime":"2018-07-05T14:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-09T09:17:16.000Z","uid":27530,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ae5c18f552e6bedd70e4a388e319a7b31fd998c0","tid":730630,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:21:13.000Z","msg":"兩電今年又加電費，為嘅就係要提高天然氣發電比例，以減少空氣污染。<br />\n<br />\n但其實發電廠位處偏僻，例如龍鼓灘發電廠、青山發電廠、南丫島發電廠等，周遭無人，加上處於香港盛行風嘅下風位，產生嘅污染物多被吹去海上，實際上對市區影響甚低；而如果發電廠係會對鄰近市區有重大影響，當初又點解要規劃係果啲地方呢？<br />\n<br />\n而且多年來推行發電廠減排，已經將既有效又低成本嘅技術使用，剩底未推行嘅多為高成本低效益嘅方法，係邊際利益下降但邊際成本急升嘅情況，點解仲要繼續無止境咁追求數字上減少排放量呢？<br />\n<br />\n最重要係，大陸飄過黎嘅污染，同香港比，真係牛脾比蚊脾，政府可唔可以更詳細公佈埋每年大概有幾多空氣污染物飄左黎香港，等大家知道下我地比咁多電費究竟改善左嘅，同大陸送黎嘅「禮」，究竟比例差幾多。"},{"pid":"5c542aa8a7afbf8a93d0e5a4b1f9bc41e71e5b22","tid":730630,"uid":18948,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T14:25:17.000Z","msg":"你啱，不過鬼叫香港痴住個撚樣國家咩"},{"pid":"927f9665e95ba2b0fc944ea368c54566a672c0f1","tid":730630,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c89b9518dd2ef4ddfaecd1c82fdbafc971e0145","tid":730630,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8249e82ab213af78605214e609dd241c8938a137","tid":730630,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6898ae3a722577fca5f352746df36ea392396c37","tid":730630,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"共享中共榮譽"},{"pid":"6c848e7240b1a4344f9261914094874155187ed0","tid":730630,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6898ae3a722577fca5f352746df36ea392396c37","tid":730630,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T15:15:18.000Z","msg":"共享中共榮譽"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-05T23:29:40.000Z","msg":"🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳🇨🇳"},{"pid":"dcdc270182802d6a331c3ebe756ab627f39698cc","tid":730630,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T06:49:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc95d0be35552d5b542ffd92715ee18e653d78da","tid":730630,"uid":80072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T07:02:08.000Z","msg":"夏天好d 冬天真係食晒小支那嘅廢氣"},{"pid":"64ca8db83d107379ec2eca1df290c607f9a7b1a9","tid":730630,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T07:05:52.000Z","msg":"之1打又話死都唔搞電網<br />\n依家大陸都唔知比左咩野你<br />\n依家又推返出黎<br />\n仲衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e9629fc2fefb04aebeb214542fe087cd0c98220","tid":730630,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"同填海起樓一樣，一日唔禁止每日150個，你填幾多海都無用。"},{"pid":"dc8bb1dcb28d14dfb69fc05399a4f8d3f162b80d","tid":730630,"uid":27530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e9629fc2fefb04aebeb214542fe087cd0c98220","tid":730630,"uid":29314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T07:15:12.000Z","msg":"同填海起樓一樣，一日唔禁止每日150個，你填幾多海都無用。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:18:13.000Z","msg":"有啲唔同，每日150個就算即時禁左，之前黎左嘅都唔會趕走，缺地事實依然存在，因為人口地係一個「累計性」問題。<br />\n<br />\n而空氣污染物，係一個「瞬間性」問題，只要停左大陸污染，空氣污染會即時解決。"},{"pid":"d39c204cb298592fb2c66f7b412ece33807508f0","tid":730630,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T08:19:30.000Z","msg":"用減廢為名 利益輸送為實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d5f806e171f582b38cb9dedfae7198d5510d1ee","tid":730630,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-08T13:42:24.000Z","msg":"再嘈改用核電"},{"pid":"e8d26acc388aded2408df528958636d4767f704f","tid"